    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nNo default mapping for `:restart`.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\n- `ZR` performs `:restart`\n- `[count]ZR` performs `:restart qall!`\n\nRationale:\n\n- Analogous to `ZZ`, `ZQ`, [ZB](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/2434).\n- \"Z\" and \"R\" are not easy to accidentally type on a qwerty keyboard.",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
    "comment_data": [
